description:
The cast and crew of Marvel Studios’ Thunderbolts* dish on their favorite scenes and juiciest spoilers from the film. Plus, we speak with Thunderbolts* composers Son Lux: Ryan Lott, Rafiq Bhatia, and Ian Chang. Later on, we’ll catch up on the comic history of the Fantastic Four’s lovable robot H.E.R.B.I.E.

00:00 - Welcome back!
1:10 - Thunderbolts* cast and crew talk fave scenes and spoilers
12:41 - Thunderbolts* composers Son Lux: Ryan Lott, Rafiq Bhatia, and Ian Chang
23:23 - H.E.R.B.I.E.'s comic book history
